metadata.title: Safco Products 1956BH Sit/Stand Bi-Level Desk, Beech/White
features: BI-LEVEL SITTING & STANDING HEIGHT DESK- Enjoy the flexibility of two, connected workstations with accommodations for multiple uses
APPEALING DESIGN- Metal and beech materials compliment each other Great addition for modern and minimalist office spaces
STANDING DESK- Adjusts from 38" to 50" high Bi-level standing-height desk Comes with adjustable foot rest
SITTING DESK- Sleek, melamine laminate 30"W top workspace
DIMENSIONS- Maximum Depth- 24" Maximum Height- 50" Maximum Width- 48" Product Weight: 56 3 lbs
description: Elevate your workspace with the elevate bi-level desk. Two different work heights, to suit a variety of workspaces. Standing Height desk adjusts from 38" to 50" high and sports an adjustable footrest for added comfort and movement while standing. Both sitting desk and standing desk provide a full 30" of workspace. Designed with a melamine laminate top and powder coated steel legs for simplicity and durability. Great for use in offices and personal workspaces.
